
**Simulate neutrino ToO**
only simulate Galactic Latitude > 10 deg

**N total** = 40 (4/year)

**Area** = 7 sq deg (one pointing)
t0 = time of trigger

* Night 0: 

    4xg @ t=t0

    1xr @ t=t0 + 15 minutes

    1xz within the night

* Night 1: 

    4xg @ t=t0

    1xr @ t=t0 + 15 minutes

* 6 <= Night <= 8:

    4xg @ t=t0

    1xr @ t=t0 + 15 minutes

* 0 <= Night <= 60: first night with u-band filter after t0
    
    1xu
